- Use pnpm:
  - `pnpm install`
  - `pnpm dev`
  - `pnpm build`
  - `pnpm lint`
- Prettier: follow shadcn style; include Tailwind plugin. Run `pnpm prettier --write .` before large edits.
- ESLint: use Next.js flat config; keep React 19/Next 15 safe patterns; fix lints before commit.
- Tailwind: utilities with class sorting via plugin; avoid custom CSS except tokens and global styles.

